8
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,000
 But why did he give me a book titled "It is OK to be Average"?

9
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
 Does that mean I am really average?

10
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,000
 I opened the book and found it quite interesting.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:50,000
 It was written by an old Chinese from Singapore,

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:53,000
 telling his life experience.

13
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:57,000
 He told a story that we are all familiar with,

14
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:59,000
