20
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:22,000
 Then, it was very sad to see a group of white ducklings.

21
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:27,000
 Its mother took the ducklings with her and walked along.

22
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:33,000
 It followed the ducklings, hoping to find a mate.

23
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:40,000
 But it was ugly, so it was always laughed at.

24
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:46,000
 "Why are you so ugly? Everyone else is white, but you are black and ugly."

25
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:52,000
