28
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:04,000
 It was more beautiful than the other ducks,

29
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,000
 and it could fly higher than them.

30
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,000
 It was a beautiful black swan,

31
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,000
