00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:32,000
 There are seven things

282
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:34,000
 you can prepare

283
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:37,000
 to make your ordinary

284
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
 become extraordinary

285
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,000
 in God.

286
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:44,000
 First,

287
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:48,000
 you have to dedicate your heart to God.

288
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
 The Bible says we should

289
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,000
 devote our heart, our mind, and our spirit

290
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,000
 to God who loves you.

291
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,000
 You have to love Him.

292
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:59,000
 You have to dedicate your heart to Him.

293
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,000
 I am willing to do so.

294
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,000
 Just like a lover,

295
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:06,000
 a wife and a husband,

296
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:08,000
 I am willing to do whatever you ask me to do.

297
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:11,000
 I will devote my heart, my spirit, and my spirit

298
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,000
 to love Him.

