00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,000
 singing,

315
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:57,000
 "Glory, glory, glory to the Jehovah of the angels."

316
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,000
 When he sees such an image,

317
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,000
 he was a normal person.

318
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,000
 God suddenly said,

319
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:08,000
 "Who can I show my love to?

320
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
 Who is willing to go for me?"

321
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,000
 He immediately said,

322
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:15,000
 "I am here. Please show me your love."

323
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:18,000
 He was ready.

324
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:22,000
 He was willing to make himself available.

325
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:25,000
 He was willing to show himself.

326
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:29,000
 This is a very important...

327
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:33,000
 But you must have a close relationship with God

328
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:35,000
 before you say this.

329
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:38,000
 "I am willing to do this for you.

330
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,000
 Please show me your love."

331
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:42,000
 Not everyone can say that.

332
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:44,000
 It must be someone you love very much.

333
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:47,000
 Your wife.

334
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
 You love her very much.

335
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,000
 What does she ask you to do?

336
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,000
 You say, "I am willing. Please show me your love."

337
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,000
 How many husbands say,

338
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:56,000
 "You and your wife ask me to show you my love."

339
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,000
 "You ask me to go shopping."

340
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,000
 "You ask me to show you my love."

341
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,000
 "You ask me to take my children to this and that."

342
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,000
 "You ask me to show you my love."

343
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:05,000
 We rarely say that.

344
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,000
 But if you really love that person,

345
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:11,000
 you are willing to do what you are willing to

346
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:15,000
 for him, for your wife, for your children.

347
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:18,000
 Besides these two things,

348
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:23,000
 the third thing is to pay attention to...

349
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:26,000
 Even if you don't have any special skills,

350
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:29,000
 you should look at what you have in your hands

351
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:32,000
 that can be used by God.

352
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:34,000
 It's like Moses.

353
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,000
 He didn't have anything. He only had a stick.

354
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,000
 He had a spear.

355
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,000
 But that spear was very powerful.

356
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:41,000
 It could turn into a snake.

357
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,000
 The snake could turn into a spear.

358
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,000
 And when it hit the water,

359
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:48,000
 it could separate the sea.

360
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:51,000
 The Red Sea was split in half

361
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,000
 and let people cross it.

362
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:57,000
 The things in his hands were not very special.

363
00:17:57,000 --> 00:18:02,000
 But they were all tools.

364
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,000
 David's spear was smaller.

365
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:07,000
 It had a stone and a rope.

366
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:11,000
 But that was also something that could be used by God.

367
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:14,000
 As long as he is willing to use you,

368
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:17,000
 you are willing to follow.

369
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:20,000
 Today, some of us have a group of sisters

370
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:22,000
 who sang very well.

371
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:25,000
 But you may say, "I don't have that voice."

372
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:29,000
 "I can hear someone singing very well."

373
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:33,000
 "Our voices are very different."

374
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:37,000
 No. You are willing to use your voice.

