00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:42,000
 Or you are willing to use your words.

376
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,000
 You may speak a few languages.

377
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:48,000
 Then you may be used by God.

378
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:51,000
 The Chaozhou dialect, Hakka dialect,

379
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:54,000
 and Cantonese,

380
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:57,000
 you may be used by God.

