00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:43,000
 I am really good at studying.

522
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:45,000
 I remember when I was in middle school,

523
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,000
 I took the first exam.

524
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:50,000
 I got 31 points out of 40 students.

525
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:54,000
 Although I didn't get to the end,

526
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:56,000
 I was already very close.

527
00:26:56,000 --> 00:27:00,000
 But when I went from the first grade to the seventh grade,

528
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:03,000
 I was the second or third in the class.

529
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:07,000
 I was slowly rising.

530
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:10,000
 I am not a very good athlete.

531
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:13,000
 I have never won a gold medal.

532
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,000
 You can see in this photo,

533
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,000
 I am playing badminton with a friend.

534
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:20,000
 You can see that he is not good at playing badminton.

535
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:23,000
 I am not a very talented person.

536
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:26,000
 At least in the eyes of a Westerner,

537
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:28,000
 I am not a very talented person.

538
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:31,000
 When I became a doctor,

539
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:35,000
 I was learning how to help people take their position.

540
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:38,000
 In the past, you had to look down like this.

541
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:45,000
 You had to look at a micro-lens to see what was in the position.

542
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:47,000
 It was very difficult.

543
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:54,000
 But the problem was that my boss didn't like me.

544
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:58,000
 He didn't like me because he thought my life was too smooth.

545
00:27:58,000 --> 00:28:01,000
 He said that I passed the exam right away.

