00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:01,000
 I am about to retire. I am in my teens.

692
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:04,000
 I don't seem to have done anything great.

693
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:06,000
 Do not underestimate your own ability.

694
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:10,000
 Because in God's eyes, it is okay to be average.

695
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:14,000
 He can make your average life

696
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:17,000
 become a very un-average life.

697
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:19,000
 Let us bow our heads and pray.

698
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:21,000
 Heavenly Father, we thank you.

699
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:27,000
 Because our life is actually under your control,

700
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:29,000
 within your plan.

701
00:37:29,000 --> 00:37:34,000
 We thank you because you allow us to enjoy

702
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:39,000
 the growth and acceptance of your love.

703
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:44,000
 Although we are not many in ability,

704
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,000
 not many in wisdom,

705
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:50,000
 you have chosen the weak in this world,

706
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:52,000
 called the wise, to be taken in.

